      "a3": "Go to Setup → Connect your TikTok account, enter your username and connect.",
      "q4": "How do I find my username?",
      "a4": "It's the name starting with @ on your TikTok profile — your unique username, not your display name.",
      "q5": "Do I have to be live?",
      "a5": "Your TikTok LIVE must be running to receive events. Use the Event Simulator to test.",
      "q6": "How do I add it to OBS?",
      "a6": "Copy the widget URL and add it as a Browser Source in OBS.",
      "q7": "My overlay isn't showing, what should I do?",
      "a7": "Check that the screen is Online, the screen number is correct and the queue isn't full.",
      "q8": "How are points earned?",
      "a8": "Through coins, shares, chat minutes and the subscriber bonus. Configure rates in Setup → Points System.",
      "q9": "Is my data safe?",
      "a9": "We never ask for your TikTok password. We only read public stream events.",
      "q10": "Can I use multiple profiles?",
      "a10": "1 stream profile on Free, 10 on PRO.",
